{"id":195363,"type":1,"name":"THE TOWN ~復讐者~","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/d8/ba/195363_993wz.jpg","summary":"　　敵は格子状の傷を持つ男。血みどろの復讐が始まる——。舞台は20キロメートル四方の小さな町、ザ・タウン。\r\n　　ここで主人公・雨木は妹を殺した仇を探し続けているのであった。手がかりはただひとつ、「格子状の傷を持つ男」。それだけ。彼の武器は復讐にたぎる血液。この血液が彼の矛と盾になるのだった。 ","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>THE TOWN ~复仇者~</li><li><span>册数: </span>2</li><li><span>话数: </span>7+2</li><li><span>作者: </span><a href=\"/person/25588\">加藤清志</a></li><li><span>出版社: </span><a href=\"/person/19306\">KADOKAWA</a>/<a href=\"/person/1581\">エンターブレイン</a></li><li><span>连载杂志: </span><a href=\"/person/8213\">ハルタ</a></li><li><span>开始: </span>2014-12-15(volume20)</li><li><span>结束: </span>2016-06-15(volume35)</li><li><span>备注: </span>从volume28起增加副标题「~復讐者~」</li>","collection":{"collect":1},"staff":[{"id":25588,"image":"","name":"加藤清志","desc":"作者"},{"id":19306,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/1c/1f/19306_prsn_x413b.jpg","name":"角川","desc":"出版社"},{"id":1581,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/51/e4/1581_prsn_U09wy.jpg","name":"enterbrain","desc":"出版社"},{"id":8213,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/63/3d/8213_prsn_9mD0D.jpg","name":"ハルタ","desc":"连载杂志"}],"comic":[{"id":195361,"name":"THE TOWN ~復讐者~ (1)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/36/b8/195361_jp.jpg"},{"id":195362,"name":"THE TOWN ~復讐者~ (2)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/43/62/195362_jp.jpg"}]}